      "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah.",
      "start": 412.199,
      "duration": 0.867
    },
    {
      "text": "You have that in Korea?",
      "start": 413.066,
      "duration": 2.633
    },
    {
      "text": "He took me to the subway but a card was required",
      "start": 415.699,
      "duration": 2.267
    },
    {
      "text": "So he took me to a nearby convenience store to buy the card",
      "start": 417.966,
      "duration": 2.634
    },
    {
      "text": "But I didn't have cash",
      "start": 420.6,
      "duration": 1.166
    },
    {
      "text": "Charge only cash...",
      "start": 421.766,
      "duration": 1.667
    },
    {
      "text": "Cash?",
      "start": 424.566,
      "duration": 0.867
    },
    {
      "text": "ATM?",
      "start": 425.433,
      "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
      "text": "I am gonna go back to the restaurant and get the money.",
      "start": 426.266,
      "duration": 3.433
    },
    {
      "text": "I am gonna go there and get it. Just stay here.",
      "start": 429.699,
      "duration": 1.034
    },
    {
      "text": "I will just give it to you for free.",
      "start": 430.733,
      "duration": 1.033
    },
    {
      "text": "* he came back with the cash *",
      "start": 431.766,
      "duration": 1.234
    },
    {
      "text": "Thank you. That's so nice of you, really. I appreciate this so much.",
      "start": 433.0,
      "duration": 3.3
    },
    {
      "text": "* I ask him via Google Translate which is better, North Korea or South Korea subway *",
      "start": 436.3,
      "duration": 3.433
    },
    {
      "text": "South Korea",
      "start": 439.733,
      "duration": 0.9
    },
    {
      "text": "South Korea?",
      "start": 440.633,
      "duration": 0.667
    },
    {
      "text": "But in North Korea...",
      "start": 441.466,
      "duration": 1.433
    },
    {
      "text": "They have a 200-meter deep subway",
      "start": 443.366,
      "duration": 0.934
    },
    {
      "text": "The North Korean army drilled down super deep fifty years ago",
      "start": 444.3,
      "duration": 6.133
    },
    {
      "text": "Yeah",
      "start": 450.433,
      "duration": 0.633
    },
    {
      "text": "* He accompanies me onto subway!!! *",
      "start": 451.933,
      "duration": 2.133
    },
    {
      "text": "It's okay, I'll go with you until your transfer station",
      "start": 454.066,
      "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
      "text": "South Korea...",
      "start": 457.733,
      "duration": 1.433
    },
    {
      "text": "Do you like South Korea?",
      "start": 461.066,
      "duration": 2.7
    },
    {
      "text": "Do you like living here?",
      "start": 464.066,
      "duration": 1.767
    },
    {
      "text": "- I like it. I like it.\n- You like it.",
      "start": 465.833,
      "duration": 2.633
    },
    {
      "text": "North Korea is a miserable place.\nPeople are starving to death right now.",
      "start": 468.466,
      "duration": 2.733
    },
    {
      "text": "He accompanied me all the way to my transfer station",
      "start": 471.199,
      "duration": 2.067
    },
    {
      "text": "To make sure I got on the right transfer",
      "start": 473.266,
      "duration": 1.467
    },
    {
      "text": "Two stations left.",
      "start": 474.733,
      "duration": 0.966
    },
    {
      "text": "* typing into Google Translate * \"Thank you...\"",
      "start": 475.699,
      "duration": 1.834
    },
    {
      "text": "so much...",
      "start": 477.533,
      "duration": 1.433
    },
    {
      "text": "Thank you so much for your help.",
      "start": 478.966,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Oh, it's a translation!",
      "start": 483.1,
      "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Wow, what a guy.",
      "start": 485.699,
      "duration": 2.167
    },
    {
      "text": "My next stop was Beijing china ",
      "start": 487.866,
      "duration": 1.934
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm about to visit Beijings only North Korean restaurant",
      "start": 489.8,
      "duration": 4.366
    },
    {
      "text": "Unlike the ones in Seoul this one is actually run by the North Korean government",
      "start": 494.166,
      "duration": 4.8
    },
    {
      "text": "And staffed entirely with people from North Korea ",
      "start": 498.966,
      "duration": 3.634
    },
    {
      "text": "Who are still in the system",
      "start": 503.433,
      "duration": 1.7
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm a little nervous coming here actually",
      "start": 505.133,
      "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
      "text": "Because I've heard they can be kind of suspicious of foreigners",
      "start": 506.633,
      "duration": 4.766
    },
    {
      "text": "And in some cases they don't let foreigners in",
      "start": 511.399,
      "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
      "text": "So I don't know if they are actually going to let me in here",
      "start": 513.833,
      "duration": 2.066
    },
    {
      "text": "And also the staff are apparently pretty weary of filming as well",
      "start": 516.7,
      "duration": 3.466
    },
    {
      "text": "All the staff are still in the system",
      "start": 520.166,
      "duration": 4.934
    },
    {
      "text": "Like, as North Koreans ",
      "start": 525.533,
      "duration": 1.467
    },
    {
      "text": "But we're going to try and see what happens",
      "start": 527.0,
      "duration": 3.299
    },
    {
      "text": "And see if I can actually order in North Korean ",
      "start": 530.299,
      "duration": 3.067
    },
    {
      "text": "So lets go",
      "start": 533.899,
      "duration": 0.534
    },
    {
      "text": "* classic, kitschy Soviet-era dining room *",
      "start": 534.433,
      "duration": 4.533
    },
    {
      "text": "[Waitress, Chinese] Hello, let me take your menu\n* Waitresses are fluent in both Chinese and Korean",
      "start": 539.366,
      "duration": 2.5
    },
    {
      "text": "[My wife, Chinese] Okay, thanks\n* Waitresses are fluent in both Chinese and Korean",
      "start": 541.866,
      "duration": 1.367
    },
    {
      "text": "We're ready to order!",
      "start": 543.233,
      "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
      "text": "So we are going to order some delicious food",
      "start": 544.433,
      "duration": 4.366
    },
    {
      "text": "Do you have potato starch noodles?\n* Very popular but casual North Korean dish",
      "start": 548.799,
      "duration": 1.667
    },
    {
      "text": "That's my favorite North Korean food",
      "start": 553.366,
      "duration": 3.3
    },
    {
      "text": "And...",
      "start": 558.866,
      "duration": 1.6
    },
    {
      "text": "What did you order?",
      "start": 560.466,
      "duration": 1.167
    },
    {
      "text": "I didn't think they would actually have it",
      "start": 564.1,
      "duration": 1.466
    },
    {
      "text": "What?",
      "start": 565.566,
      "duration": 0.8
    },
    {
      "text": "Potato starch noodles, it's a very authentic and local North Korean food",
      "start": 566.766,
      "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
      "text": "Well, I want the Pyongyang Cold Noodles*!\n* A fancier North Korean dish",
      "start": 569.866,
      "duration": 2.567
    },
    {
      "text": "So, one potato starch noodles...",
      "start": 572.433,
      "duration": 1.833
    },
    {
      "text": "That one, yes?",
      "start": 574.266,
      "duration": 0.734
    },
    {
      "text": "Yes",
      "start": 575.0,
      "duration": 0.566
    },
    {
      "text": "And a Pyongyang Cold Noodles",
      "start": 576.366,
      "duration": 1.167
    },
    {
      "text": "This one?",
      "start": 577.533,
      "duration": 1.1
    },
    {
      "text": "Yeah",
      "start": 578.866,
      "duration": 0.4
    },
    {
      "text": "This one",
      "start": 579.266,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "One Pyongyang Cold Noodles",
      "start": 579.766,
      "duration": 1.633
    },
    {
      "text": "Then I tried to order some super local North Korean street foods",
      "start": 581.399,
      "duration": 3.0
    },
    {
      "text": "That only a North Korean would know about",
      "start": 584.399,
      "duration": 1.967
    },
    {
      "text": "Do you have \"artificial meat rice\"?",
      "start": 586.366,
      "duration": 1.767
    },
    {
      "text": "No ",
      "start": 588.366,
      "duration": 0.667
    },
    {
      "text": "What about \"tofu rice\"?",
      "start": 590.366,
      "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
      "text": "No?",
      "start": 592.133,
      "duration": 0.666
    },
    {
      "text": "She's laughing!",
      "start": 594.233,
      "duration": 0.867
    },
    {
      "text": "My real favorite North Korean food is artificial meat rice",
      "start": 595.1,
      "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
      "text": "So I wanted to try that",
      "start": 598.7,
      "duration": 2.433
    },
    {
      "text": "No okay",
      "start": 601.133,
      "duration": 0.666
    },
    {
      "text": "[English] Excuse me, umm...",
      "start": 601.799,
      "duration": 1.067
    },
    {
      "text": "How many grams of noodles do you want?",
      "start": 602.866,
      "duration": 1.767
    },
    {
      "text": "Yeah? ",
      "start": 604.633,
      "duration": 0.633
    },
    {
      "text": "Yeah",
      "start": 605.266,
      "duration": 1.734
    },
    {
      "text": "My wife also wanted to try the grilled fish...",
      "start": 607.0,
      "duration": 2.066
    },
    {
      "text": "And I think that's it",
      "start": 610.033,
      "duration": 0.766
    },
    {
      "text": "Thank you",
      "start": 610.799,
      "duration": 0.667
    },
    {
      "text": "Drink?",
      "start": 611.466,
      "duration": 0.833
    },
    {
      "text": "Drink?",
      "start": 612.299,
      "duration": 0.701
    },
    {
      "text": "Do you have Taedonggang Beer? (North Korea's most famous beer brand)",
      "start": 614.033,
      "duration": 1.9
    },
    {
      "text": "Yes, we have Taedonggang Beer, Pyongyang Soju...",
      "start": 615.933,
      "duration": 2.466
    },
    {
      "text": "Ginseng tea, red ginseng tea, ginseng liquor...",
      "start": 619.433,
      "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
      "text": "Ginseng tea...",
      "start": 622.233,
      "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
      "text": "Okay, one ginseng tea, one Taedonggang Beer...",
      "start": 623.233,
      "duration": 3.566
    },
    {
      "text": "Thank you",
      "start": 626.799,
      "duration": 3.767
    },
    {
      "text": "I got a laugh out of her when I ordered the North Korean street food",
      "start": 630.566,
      "duration": 2.9
    },
    {
      "text": "Which they don't have in this restaurant",
      "start": 634.366,
      "duration": 1.667
    },
    {
      "text": "Okay so this is the beer my North Korean friends have been telling me about",
      "start": 636.033,
      "duration": 4.533
    },
    {
      "text": "Can't get it anywhere else in the world other than North Korea and right here",
      "start": 641.899,
      "duration": 4.9
    },
    {
      "text": "It's official North Korean beer",
      "start": 646.799,
      "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
      "text": "Taedonggang Beer!",
      "start": 648.299,
      "duration": 1.067
    },
    {
      "text": "Lets try",
      "start": 651.533,
      "duration": 0.766
    },
    {
      "text": "Cheers ",
      "start": 654.866,
      "duration": 1.767
    },
    {
      "text": "Not bad",
      "start": 666.933,
      "duration": 0.5
    },
    {
      "text": "Tastes kind of like Heineken ",
      "start": 668.266,
      "duration": 1.133
    },
    {
      "text": "Potato starch noodles",
      "start": 669.399,
      "duration": 1.467
    },
    {
      "text": "Pyongyang cold noodles",
      "start": 672.299,
      "duration": 1.367
    },
    {
      "text": "I would say trying North Korean food for the first time",
      "start": 675.266,
      "duration": 3.234
    },
    {
      "text": "Although by this point I've had plenty of North Korean food",
      "start": 678.5,
      "duration": 2.933
    },
    {
      "text": "Very chewy right",
      "start": 683.299,
      "duration": 1.334
    },
    {
      "text": "Honestly very good",
      "start": 685.466,
      "duration": 1.534
    },
    {
      "text": "It was kind of a surreal experience being in there",
      "start": 687.0,
      "duration": 3.1
    },
    {
      "text": "Looking at people walking around walking around with Kim Jong il pins on",
      "start": 690.1,
      "duration": 4.833
    },
    {
      "text": "What was funny was they didn't have any problems with me being American ",
      "start": 694.933,
      "duration": 4.233
    },
    {
      "text": "I thought that was going to be an issue",
      "start": 699.166,
      "duration": 1.834
    },
    {
      "text": "But it ended up not being an issue",
      "start": 701.0,
      "duration": 1.666
    },
    {
      "text": "But what was funny is my wife who is Chinese ",
      "start": 702.666,
      "duration": 4.5
    },
    {
      "text": "They asked her what was her nationality",
      "start": 707.166,
      "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
      "text": "They looked at the asian person and asked what's your nationality",
      "start": 709.766,
      "duration": 2.434
    },
    {
      "text": "And I looked it up and apparently",
      "start": 712.2,
      "duration": 1.5
    },
    {
      "text": "The issue is they are checking if you are South Korean",
      "start": 713.7,
      "duration": 1.966
    },
    {
      "text": "And if you are South Korean they will not let you into the restaurant",
      "start": 715.666,
      "duration": 4.167
    },
    {
      "text": "Which is pretty interesting",
      "start": 719.833,
      "duration": 2.133
    },
    {
      "text": "Americans I guess they don't have a problem with",
      "start": 722.533,
      "duration": 2.233
    },
    {
      "text": "Or not as much of a problem",
      "start": 724.766,
      "duration": 1.234
    },
    {
      "text": "(Wife) did you like that restaurant",
      "start": 726.0,
      "duration": 2.466
    },
    {
      "text": "What did you think about the food?",
      "start": 728.466,
      "duration": 1.3
    },
    {
      "text": "The food was great",
      "start": 730.1,
      "duration": 0.966
    },
    {
      "text": "Yeah",
      "start": 731.066,
      "duration": 0.534
    },
    {
      "text": "Did you feel it was weird being in a North Korean restaurant",
      "start": 731.6,
      "duration": 4.166
    },
    {
      "text": "Or normal?",
      "start": 735.766,
      "duration": 1.167
    },
    {
      "text": "I was fine",
      "start": 736.933,
      "duration": 0.633
    },
    {
      "text": "Well for them it's just like another day you know",
      "start": 737.566,
      "duration": 2.534
    },
    {
      "text": "I feel like it's only weird for me going as an American",
      "start": 740.1,
      "duration": 2.433
    },
    {
      "text": "For North Korean and Chinese people it's just \"yeah a North Korean restaurant\"",
      "start": 743.266,
      "duration": 3.467
    },
    {
      "text": "But you know what's kind of beautiful about it though",
      "start": 746.733,
      "duration": 2.066
    },
    {
      "text": "The staff at this place are famously non communicative with foreigners especially",
      "start": 748.799,
      "duration": 5.734
    },
    {
      "text": "I'm just glad I was able to get a laugh out of them",
      "start": 754.533,
      "duration": 1.866
    },
    {
      "text": "When I ordered the equivalent of hot dogs at the four seasons hotel, is basically what I did",
      "start": 756.399,
      "duration": 5.167
    },
    {
      "text": "I was able to make connection with somebody in the system in North Korea ",
      "start": 761.566,
      "duration": 3.7
    },
    {
      "text": "I think that's a win for the day",
      "start": 765.266,
      "duration": 1.434
    }
  ]
}